in addition to Human Rights Watch , other NGO &apos;s such as Transparency International , Oxfam , and Doctors without Borders have undergone exponential growth in terms of mainstream media mentions . by this measure , the biggest NGO &apos;s have become established players in the battle for the attention of influential editors .
